<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 13:00:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>前中央司令部司令对霍尔木兹海峡局势的坦率看法</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;退役陆军将军约瑟夫·沃特尔对如何从伊朗手中夺回霍尔木兹海峡提出了独特的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;前中央司令部指挥官对霍尔木兹海峡局势的坦率看法&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 22:13:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/former-centcom-commanders-candid-take-on-the-situation-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>印度加入欧洲战斗机计划绝非易事</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy</link><description>&lt;p&gt;印度迫切需要新型战斗机，但欧洲的下一代战斗机可能不是答案。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy"&gt;印度加入欧洲战斗机计划绝非易事&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 20:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/india-joining-one-of-europes-fighter-programs-is-anything-but-easy</guid></item><item><title>美国空军 F-35 据称被伊朗炮火击中后紧急迫降</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这架 F-35 在伊朗上空执行战斗任务时被迫转向美国空军基地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;美国空军 F-35 据称被伊朗&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;火力&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire"&gt;击中后紧急迫降&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 17:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-f-35-makes-emergency-landing-after-allegedly-being-hit-by-iranian-fire</guid></item><item><title>A-10疣猪正在霍尔木兹海峡搜寻伊朗船只</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;A-10 战斗机正在执行一项鲜为人知的任务，他们已经训练了几十年，在海峡追捕伊朗快速攻击艇和布雷层。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;A-10 疣猪在霍尔木兹海峡搜寻伊朗船只&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 16:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-prowling-for-iranian-boats-in-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>RQ-180 秘密隐形无人机似乎已紧急降落在希腊空军基地（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;希腊的观察者特别仔细地观察到了一架似乎特别神秘的无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base"&gt;RQ-180 秘密隐形无人机似乎在希腊空军基地紧急着陆（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</link><description>&lt;p&gt;南帕尔斯气田的袭击使伊朗的能源生产成为焦点，而这对伊朗政府的资金至关重要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list"&gt;伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 22:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</guid></item><item><title>驻扎在中东的美国海军扫雷舰现已抵达新加坡</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被分配执行中东扫雷任务的三艘濒海战斗舰中的两艘又向相反的方向采取了行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore"&gt;驻扎在中东的美国海军扫雷舰现已抵达新加坡后，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 19:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore</guid></item><item><title>美国使用新型 5000 磅地堡破坏者袭击伊朗反舰导弹基地：报告</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports</link><description>&lt;p&gt;GBU-72/B 位于常见的 2,000 磅掩体破坏者和更强大的 30,000 磅 GBU-57/B 大型穿甲弹之间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports"&gt;美国使用新型 5,000 磅地堡破坏者袭击伊朗反舰导弹基地：报道&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports</guid></item><item><title>海军努力维持航母的生存计划（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一艘航母在起火前就已经疲惫不堪，另一艘航母的使用寿命第二次延长，而第三艘航母的交付则被推迟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat"&gt;海军努力维持其航空母舰的生存计划（已更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</guid></item><item><title>特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在盟友拒绝向该海峡派遣军舰的要求一天后，特朗普宣布“我们不需要任何人的帮助！”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item></channel></rss>